Detailed Description

Internal OBEX message dispatcher.

This is an internal implementation class which must not be used outside APOXI OBEX at all.

Its purpose is to pick OBEX-related messages from an execution context and forward them to an ObexEventHandler instance.

void ObexDispatcher::Attach (   ) 
 

Attach to application.

Adds the ObexDispatcher to the associated execution context and registers all messages handled by the dispatcher .

void ObexDispatcher::Detach (   ) 
 

Detach from application.

Unregisters the messages handled by the ObexDispatcher and removes itself from the associated execution context.
